'''Project Decoy''' was a top-secret project attempted in [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]]. It was assigned to [[Fandar (scientist)|Fandar]] and [[Fugo]] by the [[Defense Research and Planetary Assistance Center]] and planned to create [[Human replica droid]]s for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. To the disappointment of the Rebellion, they lacked adequate funds to get a full rollout. The [[Leia Organa II|first droid]] created by the project was in the form of [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]].

The Alliance planned on making perfect replicas of Imperial officials and replacing them with the HRDs; however, they lacked sufficient funds to complete their design. Project Decoy was later fished sometime after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].<ref name="The Essential Guide to Droids">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> Parts of Project Decoy's research were used by [[Onadax Droid Technologies]] to create their new line of HRDs during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].<ref name="Or Die Trying">{{InsiderCite|75|Or Die Trying}}</ref>

